Add to this the suffocation that a woman who went for a leisurely walk got when she wanted to correct these people because of the incident, she even feared for her own life, because if such a madman attacks a dog, he may also do the same with a woman, a child, an older gentleman or probably even with anyone who is weaker than himself.
The incident occurred in a normally quiet neighborhood at five o’clock in the afternoon on an ordinary Tuesday.
The dog cried all day.
Of course, we have filed a complaint in a nearby police station, but we have great doubts whether this will bring anything at all and to prevent any prejudice from the beginning, we just want to make it clear that the cowardly criminals were Spaniards.
Our outrage at what has happened has led us to report this incident.
We cannot understand what must go on in the minds of these young people, that they find a cheap attack on a helpless animal funny, on an animal that gives us love, society and friendship.
